{"tid":700042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已婚男子兩度向14歲女露械判感化令　官寄語：勿再上咸網","createTime":"2018-06-13T04:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T20:04:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"268103fe5110975f7064a962577a2ed2e4cd8a02","tid":700042,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:31:26.000Z","msg":"已婚男子涉4日內兩度向一名14歲女生露械，男子早前承認兩項在公眾地方作猥褻行為罪，今被判15個月感化令。裁判官呼籲男子「重新嚟過，唔好再犯」，再犯案會將他狠狠重判。<br />\n<br />\n被告何浩霖（30歲）的父母及妻子均有到庭旁聽，他在庭上表示會繼續處理自己的心理問題，及反省自己做過的錯事。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官聞言對被告稱，「你第一次犯（案）我相信你」，知錯一定要改，「唔好再上啲鹹網（色情網站）」。裁判官又指，留意到被告有看精神科及心理醫生，同意被告正在改過，惟稱被告已嚇怕了事主，未知會否對事主造成心理陰影。"},{"pid":"80df625c82dc4aa7581b90556b17e0e93389d1cf","tid":700042,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180613/s00001/1528863317600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180613%2Fs00001%2F1528863317600&d=8RTelL83%2BhILtVv%2FCeYAPo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a7efb39b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180613%2Fs00001%2F1528863317600&h=d67c4e5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180613/s00001/1528863317600</a>"},{"pid":"0575d5201635cb0283977aad6dd35b6844060d57","tid":700042,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c35c32991e3d3f86a6b2639e4e02990b40da0d0d","tid":700042,"uid":79521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"On9法官 上咸網都唔撚比"},{"pid":"a7574026ef0dd4516874e05ebe08742a905fb7a7","tid":700042,"uid":74442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:37:34.000Z","msg":"唔上鹹網條友分分鐘會更變態"},{"pid":"4e7ed2a1d2836137acf649da1460d17e48c77dd2","tid":700042